243
00:18:19,969 --> 00:18:21,428
Not me!

244
00:18:21,429 --> 00:18:24,211
I ain't gonna count to three,
I'm not even gonna count to one.

245
00:18:24,273 --> 00:18:26,350
You'll shut the fuck up
or I'll sing you a lullaby!

246
00:18:26,351 --> 00:18:28,268
Shut up, man. Shut up.

247
00:18:28,269 --> 00:18:29,645
<i>There's been a mistake!</i>

248
00:18:29,646 --> 00:18:33,198
You don't understand.
I'm not supposed to be here!

249
00:18:33,199 --> 00:18:34,066
Open that cell.

250
00:18:34,067 --> 00:18:37,917
<i>Me neither. You people run
this place like a fucking prison!</i>

251
00:18:45,704 --> 00:18:47,230
Son of a bitch.

252
00:18:52,218 --> 00:18:54,382
<i>Take it easy.</i>

253
00:19:16,776 --> 00:19:20,237
If I hear so much as a mouse
fart in here the rest of the night,

254
00:19:20,238 --> 00:19:23,991
