you will all visit the infirmary.

255
00:19:23,992 --> 00:19:26,456
<i>Every last motherfucker in here.</i>

256
00:19:29,998 --> 00:19:33,747
Call the trustees.
Take that tub of shit down to the infirmary.

257
00:19:47,974 --> 00:19:52,770
<i>His first night in the joint, Andy
