274
00:22:16,998 --> 00:22:19,499
Come on. Set 'em down.
I want 'em all lined up here,

275
00:22:19,500 --> 00:22:21,777
just like a pretty little chorus line.

276
00:22:23,078 --> 00:22:24,546
Yeah, look at that!

277
00:22:24,547 --> 00:22:27,907
- Look at that. I can't stand this guy.
- Oh, Lord!

278
00:22:28,635 --> 00:22:31,386
Yes. Richmond, Virginia.

279
00:22:31,387 --> 00:22:34,555
- Smell my ass!
- After he smells mine.

280
00:22:34,556 --> 00:22:38,977
Gee, Red, it was a terrible shame
