284
00:22:48,154 --> 00:22:49,730
Lucky fuck.

285
00:22:50,331 --> 00:22:51,623
Hey, Tyrell.

286
00:22:51,824 --> 00:22:53,768
You pull infirmary duty this week?

287
00:22:54,869 --> 00:22:58,205
- How's that horse of mine doing, anyway?
